tourBios.carHigh:
Closed the 2012 season with back-to- back T-4 finishes at the TOUR Championship and The Great Waterway Classic, Played in the final group with Eugene Wong at the 2012 TOUR Championship.

Had two top-five finishes in 2011, coming in back-to- back weeks, For the second straight year, lost in a playoff at the Jane Rogers Championship ,He fell to Aaron Goldberg in 2010 and to Ryan Yip in a 3-man playoff at the 2009 event, Shot rounds of 75-72- 74-67-288 at the Florida Winter Qualifying School to earn non-exempt status for 2009, 2008 Adams Community Bank Classic Runner-Up.
tourBios.otherCarHigh: Won the 2008 Mississippi Amateur, Won the 2006 and 2004 Mississippi Match Play

dyn.dynResults: He has finished 2nd on the PGA TOUR Canada 2 times.
